                    <div class="card mt-3">
                        <h5 id="introduction" class="card-header h5 fs-2 text-center">Introduction</h5>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title fs-3">Hello!</h5>
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Welcome to CheapCarts! We are an online service that compares
                                online retail grocery prices to allow you to access food at the best price for you.
                                CheapCarts allows our users to make more informed decisions on how much food prices
                                differ between stores and allow you to make the best decision for you and your family's
                                needs. </p>
                            <p class="card-text fw-bold text-center fs-4">Let's get you started!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card mt-3">
                        <h5 id="how-to-use" class="card-header fs-2 text-center">How To Use</h5>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Our site is simple and easy to use.</p>
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">First, when you land on our <a href="/" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">home page</a>, you have three options:</p>
                            <ol>
                                <li class="fs-5">
                                    <p class="card-text fs-5">
                                    You can go to the navigation bar at the top of the screen and click <a href="/products" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">"Products"</a>,
                                    which will take you to the Products page where you can search through our
                                    selection.
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="fs-5">
                                    <p class="card-text fs-5">You can also click the "Get Started" underneath our company name, which will take you to the <a href="/products" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Products</a> page.
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="fs-5">
                                    <p class="card-text fs-5">You can hover over the first image on our site which
                                        will reveal the words "Popular Products" and a button labelled "Get Started"
                                        which will take you right to our <a href="/products" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Products</a> page.
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                
                            </ol>


                            <p class="card-text fs-5">
                            When you make it to the <a href="/products" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Product Page</a>, you can scroll through the different products that we offer. Clicking on one of the items will take to you to its individual page.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">
                            On an item's individual page, four online retail prices for the item you selected will be shown side by side and you can pick the option that is best for you. Selecting one of the retailer's card will take you directly to the item's page on the retailer's store for you to purchase.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="card my-3">
                        <h5 id="save" class="card-header fs-2 text-center">Saving Items</h5>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title fs-3">How to Save an Item</h5>
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Our customers can save different items to the <a href="/leftovers" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Leftovers</a> page,
                            which can be accessed from the navigation bar.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5 fw-bold">The Save Button looks like this:</p>
                            <!-- This button is not meant to be functional -->
                            <button class="save-btn btn btn-danger mb-3 mt-2">
                                <span class="save-label">Save </span>
                                <span class="save-heart"> <svg viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none"
                                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20">
                                        <path
                                            d="M7.5 13.5l-.354.354a.5.5 0 00.708 0L7.5 13.5zM1.536 7.536l-.354.353.354-.353zm5-5l-.354.353.354-.353zM7.5 3.5l-.354.354a.5.5 0 00.708 0L7.5 3.5zm.964-.964l-.353-.354.353.354zm-.61 10.61L1.889 7.182l-.707.707 5.964 5.965.708-.708zm5.257-5.964l-5.965 5.964.708.708 5.964-5.965-.707-.707zM6.182 2.889l.964.965.708-.708-.965-.964-.707.707zm1.672.965l.964-.965-.707-.707-.965.964.708.708zM10.964 1c-1.07 0-2.096.425-2.853 1.182l.707.707A3.037 3.037 0 0110.964 2V1zM14 5.036c0 .805-.32 1.577-.89 2.146l.708.707A4.036 4.036 0 0015 5.036h-1zm1 0A4.036 4.036 0 0010.964 1v1A3.036 3.036 0 0114 5.036h1zM4.036 2c.805 0 1.577.32 2.146.89l.707-.708A4.036 4.036 0 004.036 1v1zM1 5.036A3.036 3.036 0 014.036 2V1A4.036 4.036 0 000 5.036h1zm.89 2.146A3.035 3.035 0 011 5.036H0c0 1.07.425 2.096 1.182 2.853l.707-.707z"
                                            fill="currentColor"></path>
                                    </svg></span>
                            </button>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">In order to save an item, you can click the red heart button on
                                the bottom right corner of the item card on the <a href="/products" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Product Page</a> or
                                below the item name on its individual product page.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">After you save the item, you can see it on the <a href="/leftovers" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Leftovers</a> page.</p>

                            <hr>
        
                            <h5 id="leftovers-info" class="card-title fs-3 my-3 mt-3">Leftovers Page</h5>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">On the <a href="/leftovers" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Leftovers</a> page, you can several things with your saved items.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">You can remove items from your <a href="/leftovers" class="guide-link text-Cambridge link-underline link-underline-opacity-0">Leftovers</a> by clicking the "Trash" button on each item. </p>

                            <p class="card-text fw-bold fs-5">The Trash Button looks like this:</p>
                            <button type="button" class="mb-2 btn btn-danger">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19" height="19"><path d="M4.5 3V1.5a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 011 1V3M0 3.5h15m-13.5 0v10a1 1 0 001 1h10a1 1 0 001-1v-10M7.5 7v5m-3-3v3m6-3v3" stroke="currentColor"></path></svg>
                            </button>


                            <p class="card-text fs-5 mt-3">You can also clear all of your Leftovers by clicking the button in the top right hand corner.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fw-bold fs-5">The Clear All Button looks like this: </p>
                            <button type="button" id="save-clear" class="m-2 btn btn-danger" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#clearItemsModal">
                                    <span class="clear-label">Clear All</span>
                                    <span class="clear-icon">
                                    <svg viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22"><path d="M1.5 1.5l12 12m-12 0l12-12" stroke="currentColor"></path></svg>
                                    </span>
                            </button>


                        </div>
                    </div>
